                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300114-186-off996 t18300114-186-crimeloc999"></join>. Between one and two o'clock on the 21st of December, I saw the prisoner reach over the board, and take this beef from a fore-quarter of beef; I went to the door, and hallooed Stop thief! - I saw him about twenty yards from the door; the meat was then on the ground - I saw him stopped, without losing sight of him.</p>
